{
  "texts": [
    "Nevertheless, the black market has expanded globally with the advent of the dark web [11].",
    "Thus, whoever wants to participate in the black market can do so without following the laws.",
    "As a result, black markets on the dark web pose significant threats to individuals, governments, and businesses.Illegal products, services, and content are traded on the dark web [12,13].",
    "For example, drugs, weapons, counterfeit goods, and stolen information are all available for purchase and sale on the dark web.",
    "In addition, identities, financial fraud, and other illegal activities can be performed using stolen information, particularly among cybercriminals."
  ]
}